name: Dr Shea Reen Tey 妇产科 /生育医生[ObStetrics and Gynaecology] [Fertility Specialist]

reviews.text: My wife had the C section for our third child with her and she did tremendous job on the surgery itself and thoroughly checking up with her condition even a year after. She showed genuine care for her patients and always making sure that her patients are comfortable. Thanks so much, Dr. Tey.

Really happy with my experience with Dr. Tey Sheareen! She was super gentle and explained everything clearly during my baby scan. Felt very reassured and comfortable throughout. Thank you for being so kind and patient, Dr. Tey!

I had my LSCS operation with Dr. Tey Shea Reen and I’m very happy with the results. The wound was stitched so neatly that there’s barely any scar visible. Dr. Goh Chuan Yong was also very friendly and gave clear, detailed explanations that were easy for us as parents to understand. I highly recommend seeing Dr. Tey Shea Reen for pregnancy follow-ups and delivery. She’s truly excellent.
Had my first born via C section by Dr Tey. A great experience with Dr Tey throughout my pregnancy. She is professional, caring and friendly. Highly recommended!

Clinic was so crowded, waited for such a long time, it was all worth it in the end. Consultation was cheerful, the procedures were painless, barely felt the "stick" from below. I feel very comfortable with Dr Tey.
